        |  </body>
        | </html>
      .pull-left
        a.eventable.btn.btn-success.btn-large.qs-step5-act &laquo; Prev 
      .pull-right
        a.eventable.btn.btn-success.btn-large.qs-stepFinal-act Finish &raquo;
    .qs-stepFinal(style='display: none;')
      h2 Use It!
      p Open the command console and run the following commands:
      pre
        | statechart.sendEvent('firstEvent');
      .pull-right
        a.eventable.btn.btn-success.btn-large(href='./quick-start.html') Working Demo &raquo;
